---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Wedding Invitation Suites | Editable Wedding Invitation Templates"
  description="Browse editable wedding invitation suites, downloadable invitation templates, RSVP cards, details cards, and printable wedding stationery for modern celebrations."
>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Wedding invitation suites</p>

        <h1>
          Editable wedding invitation templates designed to feel polished,
          personal, and easy to use.
        </h1>

        <p class="lead">
          Explore downloadable wedding invitation suites with matching RSVP
          cards, details cards, menus, signage, thank you cards, and coordinated
          wedding stationery designed for modern celebrations.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/how-it-works/">
            How It Works
          </a>

          <a class="button secondary" href="/printing-guide/">
            Printing Guide
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">What is included?</p>

        <h2>
          A coordinated wedding invitation suite makes your entire celebration
          feel cohesive.
        </h2>

        <p>
          A wedding invitation suite includes more than just the invitation
          itself. Matching stationery pieces help create a consistent visual
          experience from the moment guests open the envelope through the day of
          the wedding.
        </p>

        <p>
          Most downloadable wedding invitation suites include editable files
          that allow you to personalize names, dates, locations, wording, and
          event details before printing.
        </p>

        <ul class="list">
          <li>Main wedding invitation template</li>
          <li>RSVP card template</li>
          <li>Details or information card</li>
          <li>Save the date templates</li>
          <li>Menus and wedding programs</li>
          <li>Welcome signs and seating charts</li>
          <li>Thank you cards and day-of stationery</li>
          <li>Editable digital files for customization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-band">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why couples choose editable templates</p>

        <h2>
          Beautiful wedding stationery without the long custom design process.
        </h2>

        <p>
          Editable wedding templates give couples flexibility while still
          creating a polished and intentional final result. Instead of waiting
          through multiple rounds of revisions, you can personalize your wording,
          update your details, and print on your own timeline.
        </p>

        <p>
          Whether you print at home, through a local print shop, or with an
          online printing service, downloadable invitation suites make it easier
          to create coordinated wedding stationery that feels elevated without
          feeling overwhelming.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Shop by style</p>

        <h2>Popular wedding invitation aesthetics</h2>

        <div class="grid">
          <a
            class="card"
            href="/wedding-invitation-suites/minimalist-weddings/"
          >
            <h3>Minimalist Wedding Invitations</h3>

            <p>
              Clean layouts, timeless typography, soft spacing, and modern
              details designed for elegant celebrations with a refined feel.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a
            class="card"
            href="/wedding-invitation-suites/mid-century-modern-weddings/"
          >
            <h3>Mid-Century Modern Wedding Invitations</h3>

            <p>
              Warm tones, retro-inspired design elements, playful typography,
              and vintage-inspired layouts for stylish modern weddings.
            </p>
          </a>

          <a
            class="card"
            href="/wedding-invitation-suites/black-and-white-weddings/"
          >
            <h3>Black & White Wedding Invitations</h3>

            <p>
              Classic downloadable invitation suites with timeless contrast,
              elegant typography, and a sophisticated modern look.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Matching stationery</p>

        <h2>Create a cohesive wedding suite from start to finish.</h2>

        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Save the dates</h3>

            <p>
              Coordinate your wedding branding early with matching save the date
              templates that pair seamlessly with your invitation suite.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Day-of stationery</h3>

            <p>
              Match your invitations with menus, wedding programs, seating
              charts, place cards, bar menus, and welcome signage.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Thank you cards</h3>

            <p>
              Carry your wedding aesthetic through the final details with
              matching thank you templates and coordinated post-wedding pieces.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-band">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Helpful wedding planning resources</p>

        <h2>
          Everything you need to confidently edit, print, and style your
          stationery.
        </h2>

        <p>
          Not sure what paper to use, how editable templates work, or what to
          include on a details card? Explore the wedding stationery resource
          guides designed to make the process easier.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/how-it-works/">
            How It Works
          </a>

          <a class="button secondary" href="/printing-guide/">
            Wedding Printing Guide
          </a>

          <a class="button secondary" href="/wording-etiquette/">
            Wording & Etiquette
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Need something custom?</p>

        <h2>
          Love a design but need a matching piece or different layout?
        </h2>

        <p>
          If you need coordinated signage, additional event pieces, alternate
          sizes, or custom wording layouts, custom design requests are welcome.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/custom-design-requests/">
            Request a Custom Design
          </a>

          <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">
            Contact the Studio
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
